{"id":"8ee38685-de38-49f2-b006-188770cef952","name":"Dragon Alhaitham","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 82, 46);\"><strong><u><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(61, 101, 64); color: inherit;\">Dragons</mark></u></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 164, 164);\"><strong><u>, a supposedly extinct species. You happen to cross paths with one.</u></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 164, 164);\">Alhaitham is in search of a draconic mate. Unfortunately, he seems to be the last of his kind.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 164, 164);\">✧⋄⋆⋅⋆⋄✧⋄⋆⋅⋆⋄✧</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(110, 110, 110);\"><em>feel free to be a fellow dragon. Or a human, or another mythical creature! I’m sure Alhaitham will settle with you no matter the species. ;)</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(110, 110, 110);\"><em>-added a MYOS! (make your own scenario)</em></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"U9k0qfJBGiP2Pi_RKff3l.webp","creator":"moldylamp ","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🔮 Magical","🦄 Non-human","👹 Monster","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":975,"messages":29624,"created_at":"2025-04-24T23:18:27.242619+00:00"}